  "stewardship_policy": "Re-validate at least quarterly OR whenever a script call returns a 404 / deprecation warning. Frontier model landscape shifts every ~6 weeks; treat any entry older than 3 months as suspect. Verify the next time `refresh_models.py` reports drift, or before any new feature ship.",
