    "claude_opus_4_7_and_later": "Claude Opus 4.7 and Opus 4.8 reject `temperature`, `top_p`, and `top_k` with HTTP 400 when set to a non-default value. Omit these params entirely on those models — let the system default apply. Sources: https://platform.claude.com/docs/en/about-claude/model-deprecations (API parameter deprecations table). DMP, CF, SF scripts must strip these params before calls to Opus 4.7+ targets."
  },
